						               													<description>Welcome to the days of old, when knights were bold!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Medieval Mayhem is a family-friendly and simple but addictive card game &amp;ndash; a crazy mash of humor, kings, strategy, caricatures, wizards, bluffing, puns, randomness and other nonsense...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Split your hand of ten debatably brave characters into five powerful armies and let them loose on your friends!! Before the battle starts, you will also have a betting round: the perfect opportunity to bluff and deceive the other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Here is the recipe for creating Medieval Mayhem: mix Exploding Kittens and Poker, add Hugo's crazy cartoons and Andreea's charming watercolors, sprinkle a Medieval theme (and puns!) onto it, balance the flavors so that it can be enjoyed by kids and grown-ups and by casual and serious players alike, et voila - you now have Medieval Mayhem!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash; description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
